# ============================================================
# Rust API - Mục lục HTTP Test (REST Client / VS Code)
# Các request đã được tách thành từng file trong thư mục requests/
# ============================================================
#
# Danh sách file:
#   requests/health.http      - Health check
#   requests/auth.http        - Register, Login, Get me
#   requests/users.http       - Users CRUD, assign/revoke role
#   requests/profile.http     - Me profile GET/PUT
#   requests/roles.http       - Roles CRUD, permissions của role
#   requests/permissions.http - Permissions CRUD
#   requests/media.http       - Media upload, list, CRUD, bulk-delete
#   requests/settings.http    - Settings list, get, update
#   requests/banners.http     - Banners list active, get by key, CRUD
#   requests/banner-items.http - Banner items CRUD
#   requests/categories.http - Categories list, get by slug, CRUD
#   requests/tags.http        - Tags list, get by slug, CRUD
#   requests/posts.http       - Posts list, get by slug, CRUD
#   requests/languages.http  - Languages list, default
#   requests/audit-logs.http  - Audit logs list
#   requests/admin.http       - Admin dashboard
#
# Biến chung: requests/_env.http (host, contentType, authToken)
# ============================================================
